---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header title={SITE_TITLE} />
		<main>
			<h1>SIM IT Club</h1>
			<div class="center">
				<img width="720" height="360" src="/simitc-banner.jpg" class='light-only' alt="" />
				<img width="720" height="360" src="/simitc-banner.jpg" class='dark-only' alt="" />
			</div>
			<p>
				Hey there 👋<br />
				We're the SIM Information Technology Club (ITC) — the hangout spot for techies,
				curious minds, and “I’ll-learn-as-I-go” folks. Here, we build cool stuff,
				learn useful things, and just vibe together. ✨
			</p>
			<p>
				Our mission? Keep tech fun, relevant, and useful — no gatekeeping, no
				stress. 🚀
			</p>
			<p>Throughout the year, we run a mix of events and initiatives:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>🧠 Tech talks & seminars with industry experts</li>
				<li>🧪 Hands-on workshops in Web Dev, GitHub, AI, UI/UX & more</li>
				<li>🎉 Hackathons (yes, the fun kind)</li>
			</ul>
			<br />

			<div class="center">
				<img width="720" height="360" src="/how-to-get-involved-banner.jpg" class='light-only' alt="" />
				<img width="720" height="360" src="/how-to-get-involved-banner.jpg" class='dark-only' alt="" />
			</div>
			<p>
				👉 First step: <br />Join our <a
					href="https://t.me/+o_3QtjEFmNFhYmFl"
					target="_blank">Telegram group</a
				>! We’ll share tech-related content like hackathon alerts, upcoming tech events in Singapore, and updates on SIM IT Club’s own activities.
				No harm in joining — just do it. 😉
			</p>

			<p>
				👉 <b>SIM ITCLUB EXCO RECRUITMENT 26/27 IS NOW OPEN!</b> 🚨<br />
				Want to build real leadership experience outside of the classroom? This is your chance to lead teams, manage projects, and grow alongside driven people - while creating a meaningful impact and helping build a thriving community. 💡
			</p>

			<div class="center">
				<img width="720" height="900" src="/exco-recruitment-26-27.png" alt="SIM IT Club EXCO Recruitment 26/27 Poster" />
			</div>

			<p>
				If you've ever wanted to make a real difference, this is where it starts. SIM IT Club is looking for passionate students to join the 26/27 EXCO team and give back to the IT community!
			</p>

			<p><b>🔓 Roles Available:</b></p>
			<ul>
				<li>President</li>
				<li>Vice President</li>
				<li>General Secretary</li>
				<li>Finance & Logistics Secretary</li>
				<li>Technical Director (Internal)</li>
				<li>Technical Director (External)</li>
				<li>Marketing Director</li>
				<li>Partnership & Innovation Director</li>
			</ul>

			<p>
				🕒 Applications closes on <b>16 May 2026, 2359 SGT</b><br />
				📍 Apply via <a href="https://forms.office.com/pages/responsepage.aspx?id=eF0ERJXMGE2FJ2YvtdVEB5U1GPMULWxBsRS9u5MtoPJUNTBKN0tCM0JPRVQxVzkyRUUwM1QzWUJVUi4u&route=shorturl" target="_blank">this form</a>!
				(Full job descriptions <a href="https://canva.link/0oiwsqdiy0pq8xg" target="_blank">here</a> ✍️)
			</p>

			<p>
				We're also proud to be part of the student chapter under the Singapore
				Computer Society (SCS) 🏢 and Association of Information Security
				Professionals (AISP) 🔐.
			</p>
		</main>

		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
